markets.title: Gladiator 2 Rotten Tomatoes score?
markets.subtitle: Above 72
markets.rules_primary: If Gladiator 2 has a Tomatometer score of above 72 on Nov 25, 2024 at 10:00AM ET, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: Update 12:00 AM ET 3/5/24: Originally these markets were created with fixed dates at which they expire; however, we're concerned about the impact a delay in release date would have on the markets. We're filing an amendment today to extend the Last Trading and Expiration Dates to following the wide release of the film, whenever that is.
